</head>
<body>

  <h1>Explore the Web</h1>
  <p>Here are some of the most amazing websites on the internet. Click any link to visit!</p>

  <h2>Learn Something New</h2>
  <p>Visit <a href="https://www.wikipedia.org/">Wikipedia</a> — the world's largest free encyclopaedia.</p>
  <p>Discover books that change the way you think at <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/">Goodreads</a> — the world's largest community of readers sharing books about life, courage, and wisdom.</p>

  <h2>Explore Space</h2>
  <p>Discover the universe at <a href="https://www.nasa.gov/">NASA</a> — live rocket launches, Mars missions and more.</p>
  <p>See the deepest images of space at <a href="https://webb.nasa.gov/">James Webb Space Telescope</a>.</p>

  <h2>Explore Earth</h2>
  <p>Explore a live 3D view of our planet at <a href="https://eyes.nasa.gov/apps/earth/">NASA Eyes on the Earth</a> — an interactive 3D globe showing real satellites orbiting Earth right now, built by NASA.</p>
  <p>Discover nature and wildlife at <a href="https://www.nationalgeographic.com/">National Geographic</a>.</p>

</body>
</html>

